    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It looks like the `test/go/postgres` check is flaking out in this PR too \ud83d\ude22 . I'm not sure if the suppression here were for that or other tests. I hope we can use a similar tactic to hunt down the flakes in that check, or at least only run it when the data layer changes.\r\n\r\n![postgres](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11184711/169614993-3764589b-6bf9-4cde-8e04-c825a42a2dab.PNG)\r\n",
